{"tid":1127471,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"整左個簡文書機考慮， 希望比d意見","createTime":"2019-04-27T06:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T04:14:10.000Z","uid":90323,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fc3ad114a5b6f81d106cd1e39d0be83b72e4f9ad","tid":1127471,"uid":90323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:43:46.000Z","msg":"呼,簡左2次電腦第二次幫人簡。<br />\n希望寫點總結:<br />\n<br />\n一部電腦，最貴最要考慮的係CPU 和電腦牌子(即底板 火牛的配合)，<br />\n其他係可以加加減減嘅，差唔到幾百。<br />\n<br />\n而，根據最耐用報告，<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/03/24/computerrepair/notebook/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2Fcomputerrepair%2Fnotebook%2F&d=wHiIeFeeqtLxwJ75m5qcs%2B2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=a1958efe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/03/24/computerrepair/notebook/</a><br />\nSamsung, apple, lenovo 嘅thinkpad(其他系列風評一般), dell, surface, 我會加上fujitsu同埋toshiba呢2個日本牌子, 都係較耐用嘅。 呢D牌子敢出3年保養,<br />\n<br />\n而，文書機嘅話，又想平，就要堅持i3, i5 呢D CPU, 唔好比人說服買更高嘅。<br />\n例如，我簡I3做文書機，而家出到差唔多第9代，咁我會接受6代至9代，<br />\n即結尾係 i3-6xxx to i3-9xxx呢D機。<br />\n<br />\n定死左呢2個frame，就可以諗其他。<br />\n<br />\n跟住係重量，15.6&quot; (傾向最大MON量產系列)一定較重嘅。<br />\n其他網站catalogue 唔清晰，dell 的最清，所以介紹dell<br />\n主要係inspiration 較為輕， 15.6&rdquo;  重量主要係2-2.2kg 14&rdquo; 重量主要係 1.5kg<br />\n<br />\n所以如果比我買新，我會簡I3-8xxx 15.6&rdquo;, <a href=\"http://跟住上price.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%B7%9F%E4%BD%8F%E4%B8%8Aprice.com.hk&d=wHiIeFeeqtLxwJ75m5qcs%2B2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=89554654\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">跟住上price.com.hk</a>(最好的電子格價網) 睇巿價, <br />\n主要睇4-5星級商戶的行貨報價去比價。<br />\n<br />\n咁就可以簡到去邊到買最平喇.<br />\n<br />\n其實而家個網站賣機系統都唔太好， 要人睇一堆資料， 睇半日咁去諗，sell 就一心sell 舊嘅高配硬件， 希望有一日會改善。"},{"pid":"edeb22ecbe0b562a066113a670660c7da67e3e8d","tid":1127471,"uid":197609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc3ad114a5b6f81d106cd1e39d0be83b72e4f9ad","tid":1127471,"uid":90323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"20