。<br />\n4G ram,...?<br />\n好似唔駛呢個價喎， 有冇講錯。<br />\n<br />\nadd self即係你自已再加？<br />\n<br />\n7千幾應該有獨顯喎， 咁唔駛買i5?"},{"pid":"6ff64dce22a02cff073e1c9a80cf28b758c56446","tid":1127471,"uid":179672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T00:41:44.000Z","msg":"Notebook 其實主要硬件外好多野都好重要<br />\n尤其文書機<br />\n鏡面定霧面mon，色水，解像度<br />\nKeyboard 有冇燈岩唔岩打<br />\nTouchpad 岩唔岩你<br />\n有冇需要 numpad果欄<br />\nUsb 位多？ 有冇sd卡位之類<br />\n電量等等<br />\n<br />\n人人岩既野都唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09913fa1a6da053e8f546f664144d130c4c3db6d","tid":1127471,"uid":60249,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T01:15:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c952135f1ce65596252a7909622f80f42b7f0dd0","tid":1127471,"uid":1123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T01:40:46.000Z","msg":"文書機 = Notebook<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f255429c504827d07ccaba38f23ad66a735167c1","tid":1127471,"uid":131430,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T02:19:21.000Z","msg":"講咁多 不如list 幾部出黎仲易明"},{"pid":"8cb8212ce2d7125ae90e827fedf6abf2da42c2a6","tid":1127471,"uid":90323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f255429c504827d07ccaba38f23ad66a735167c1","tid":1127471,"uid":131430,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T02:19:21.000Z","msg":"講咁多 不如list 幾部出黎仲易明"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T03:50:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dell.com/zh-hk/shop/dell-筆記型電腦/inspiron-15-3000/spd/inspiron-15-3583-laptop/configurations\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dell.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fshop%2Fdell-%E7%AD%86%E8%A8%98%E5%9E%8B%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%2Finspiron-15-3000%2Fspd%2Finspiron-15-3583-laptop%2Fconfigurations&d=wHiIeFeeqtLxwJ75m5qcs%2B2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=d92bad71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dell.com/zh-hk/shop/dell-筆記型電腦/inspiron-15-3000/spd/inspiron-15-3583-lap